quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  43,36,"Whoever shuns the remembrance of the Most Gracious, We assign for him a devil, to be his companion"
  43,37,"They hinder them from the path, though they think they are guided"
  43,38,"Until, when He comes to Us, he will say, “If only there were between me and you the distance of the two Easts.” What an evil companion"
  43,39,"It will not benefit you on that Day, since you did wrong. You are partners in the suffering"
  43,40,"Can you make the deaf hear, or guide the blind, and him who is in evident error"
  43,41,"Even if We take you away, We will wreak vengeance upon them"
  43,42,Or show you what We have promised them; for We have absolute power over them
  43,43,So adhere to what is revealed to you. You are upon a straight path
  43,44,"It is a message for you, and for your people; and you will be questioned"
  43,45,"Ask those of Our messengers We sent before you: “Did We appoint gods besides the Most Gracious to be worshiped?”"